ly emits ultrasonic waves from its mouth to check its sur\u00ad roundings."},{"version":"silver","text":"Capable of flying safely in dark places, it emits ultrasonic cries to check for any obstacles."},{"version":"crystal","text":"During the day, it gathers with others and hangs from the ceilings of old buildings and caves."},{"version":"ruby","text":"ZUBAT remains quietly unmoving in a dark spot during the bright daylight hours. It does so because prolonged exposure to the sun causes its body to become slightly burned."},{"version":"sapphire","text":"ZUBAT avoids sunlight because exposure causes it to become unhealthy. During the daytime, it stays in caves or under the eaves of old houses, sleeping while hanging upside down."},{"version":"emerald","text":"While living in pitch-black caverns, their eyes gradually grew shut and deprived them of vision. They use ultrasonic waves to detect obstacles."},{"version":"firered","text":"It has no eyes. Instead, it relies on its ultrasonic cries for echo location to flit about in darkness."},{"version":"leafgreen","text":"It forms colonies in perpetually dark  places and uses ultrasonic waves to   identify and approach targets."},{"version":"diamond","text":"Even though it has no eyes, it can sense obstacles using ultrasonic waves it emits from its mouth."},{"version":"pearl","text":"Disliking sunlight, it sleeps deep in forests and caves until sundown."},{"version":"platinum","text":"It checks its surroundings and location using reflections of the ultrasonic waves from its mouth."},{"version":"heartgold","text":"While flying, it constantly emits ultrasonic waves from its mouth to check its surroundings."},{"version":"soulsilver","text":"Capable of flying safely in dark places, it emits ultrasonic cries to check for any obstacles."},{"version":"black","text":"It checks its surroundings and location using reflections of the ultrasonic waves from its mouth."},{"version":"white","text":"It checks its surroundings and location using reflections of the ultrasonic waves from its mouth."},{"version":"black-2","text":"It does not need eyes, because it emits ultrasonic waves to check its surroundings while it flies."},{"version":"white-2","text":"It does not need eyes, because it emits ultrasonic waves to check its surroundings while it flies."},{"version":"x","text":"Even though it has no eyes, it can sense obstacles using ultrasonic waves it emits from its mouth."},{"version":"y","text":"It has no eyes. Instead, it relies on its ultrasonic cries for echolocation to flit about in darkness."},{"version":"omega-ruby","text":"Zubat remains quietly unmoving in a dark spot during the bright daylight hours. It does so because prolonged exposure to the sun causes its body to become slightly burned."},{"version":"alpha-sapphire","text":"Zubat avoids sunlight because exposure causes it to become unhealthy. During the daytime, it stays in caves or under the eaves of old houses, sleeping while hanging upside down."},{"version":"sun","text":"It sleeps in caves during the day. It has no eyes, so to check its surroundings while flying, it emits ultrasonic waves."},{"version":"moon","text":"When exposed to sunlight, they suffer burns. The frequency of their ultrasonic waves can differ slightly from colony to colony."},{"version":"ultra-sun","text":"It has no eyeballs, so it can\u2019t see. It checks its surroundings via the ultrasonic waves it emits from its mouth."},{"version":"ultra-moon","text":"Their skin is so thin that they\u2019ll be burned if sunlight hits them. When it gets cold out, they gather together to warm one another\u2019s bodies."},{"version":"lets-go-pikachu","text":"Emits ultrasonic cries while it flies. They act as a sonar used to check for objects in its way."},{"version":"lets-go-eevee","text":"Emits ultrasonic cries while it flies. They act as a sonar used to check for objects in its way."},{"version":"sword","text":"It emits ultrasonic waves from its mouth to check its surroundings. E